There are just a few days before the @APISpecs CFP closes at end of day June 3rd: events.linuxfoundation.org/openapi-asc/pr…

If you identify as non-male and have any ideas around using API specifications (OpenAPI, gRPC, GraphQL, AsyncAPI, JSON Schema, etc) *for anything*, I will help you submit!
